{"id":643976,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/【立此存照】只因太像习近平？歌唱家刘克清形/","date":"2020-05-12T17:41:41Z","modified":"2020-05-12T17:49:29Z","title":"【立此存照】只因太像习近平？歌唱家刘克清“形象违规”遭封号","content":"<p>5月12日，网传著名男中音歌唱家刘克清因“长相酷似习近平”自去年9月以来在抖音短视频平台遭遇多次封号，官方解释为“形象违规”，期间刘克清本人不得不多次提交个人证明材料，并向网友求助。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643985\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXz-fgoU8AA2EHx-e1589305621493.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"460\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXz-fgoU8AA2EHx-e1589305621493.jpeg 524w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXz-fgoU8AA2EHx-e1589305621493-261x300.jpeg 261w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p>从刘克清本人的描述看，他遭遇的三次封号与网友评论并点赞（习近平名字）触发敏感词、个人头像遭人举报有关：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643980\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/image_from_ios.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"866\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/image_from_ios.jpg 604w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/image_from_ios-156x300.jpg 156w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/image_from_ios-532x1024.jpg 532w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643981\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXzvK4qUMAA0MVe-e1589304760965.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"619\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXzvK4qUMAA0MVe-e1589304760965.jpeg 388w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EXzvK4qUMAA0MVe-e1589304760965-218x300.jpeg 218w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>目前，刘克清的抖音账号恢复，但已将酷似习近平的个人头像进行了修改：</p>\n<p>原头像：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643984\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/刘克清.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/刘克清.png 498w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/刘克清-300x242.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p>新头像：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643986\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/刘克清2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/刘克清2.png 578w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/刘克清2-300x233.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p>频道页面：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-643982\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EX0TexSU0AA_AME-e1589304732236.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"407\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EX0TexSU0AA_AME-e1589304732236.jpeg 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EX0TexSU0AA_AME-e1589304732236-300x244.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EX0TexSU0AA_AME-e1589304732236-1024x833.jpeg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EX0TexSU0AA_AME-e1589304732236-768x625.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/EX0TexSU0AA_AME-e1589304732236-1080x878.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">刘克清，著名男中音歌唱家、歌剧表演艺术家，奥地利蒂诺尔州歌剧院、德国节尔州国家剧院全职驻院独唱演员，曾主演歌剧50余部。 ——  百度百科</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-643978\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/48540923dd54564e1d3ddfecb5de9c82d0584f8e.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"196\" height=\"274\" /></p>\n<p>有网友认为，刘克清不但“长相酷似习近平”，连声音也有几分相似。然而，因长相而成为“违规”确实是首次见。</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"男歌唱家刘克清在网上教唱歌，因长得像习近平，账号被抖音封锁。\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/yPFKUhJdqzk?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">中国旅欧男中音歌唱家刘克清，用抖音传授唱歌知识，因“头像违规”现还在审核中，他就那么丑吗？……[坏笑][坏笑] <a href=\"https://t.co/tm5q5faIZE\">pic.twitter.com/tm5q5faIZE</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 戴维（英国观察） (@david_david1968) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/david_david1968/status/1260159775175835650?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 12, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><strong>以下为中国数字时代编辑摘自部分网友评论：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>@Mo*****4269：他的容貌涉嫌颠覆社会主义政权。</p>\n<p>@Jac*****149：长得有点寻衅滋事&#8230;..</p>\n<p>@co*****9cn：声乐分几种唱法？</p>\n<p>@CC*****068：长得太包。</p>\n<p>@mrF*****t2Pk：在朝鮮打飽嗝就是違規，在中國長得像就是違規。</p>\n<p>@Gi*****7：这哥们唱的不错，可惜长相没能避讳。</p>\n<p>@coi*****ian：好无辜的躺枪。</p>\n<p>@kil*****p6：这才艺能秒1000个小学生！</p>\n<p>@chi*****2019：本朝新制，相貌避諱！</p>\n<p>@wa*****nli：有权真好，不仅名字忌讳，肖像也忌讳，赞美不起劲也该抓起来批斗了吧！</p></blockquote>\n","author":1069,"categories":[18271,38912,39486,38918],"tags":[13222,40518,40517,30382,40519,40521,40520,16934]}